10 Waves, 3 Months, One Goal: Mainnet Deployment
Each Wave follows a 14-day build cycle:

Build Phase (10 days)
Integrate or deepen your Aleo integration
Ship new features, UX improvements, and smart contract logic
Move from testnet toward mainnet
Run experiments: users, traction, and integrations
Evaluation Phase (4 days)
Judges review and score based on:

Privacy implementation and ZK capabilities
Product quality and UX
Innovation and creativity
Progress and iteration
