Build Privacy-Preserving Apps Across Every Vertical
Aleo's zero-knowledge architecture enables privacy in any application. Here are high-impact verticals where your innovation can shine:

üí∞ Private Finance (DeFi)
Private Prediction Markets
Private Trading & Liquidity
Shielded AMMs and DEXs ‚Äî Positions, balances, and order sizes stay confidential.
Private Limit Orders, TWAP, or RFQ Systems ‚Äî Eliminate MEV and front-running.
Smart Routers ‚Äî Keep order routing logic and execution details hidden.
Dark Pools ‚Äî Institutional-grade privacy on large trades.
Privacy-Preserving Credit & Lending
Undercollateralized Loans ‚Äî Borrowers prove creditworthiness via ZK proofs.
Private Onchain Credit Scores ‚Äî Verifiable but not fully transparent.
ZK-based Eligibility Checks ‚Äî KYC, jurisdiction, and whitelisting without exposing raw data.
Cross-Chain Private Yield & Structured Products
Private Yield Vaults‚Äî Fueled by liquidity bridged from other chains.
Exotic DeFi Products ‚Äî Options, tranches, rate products where individual positions remain private but system solvency is provable.
Strategy Aggregators ‚Äî Hide per-user allocations while proving fair execution.
Institutional & Treasury DeFi
Treasury Tools ‚Äî For funds, DAOs, and companies to keep strategies private while offering ZK proofs for compliance.
Private Payroll and B2B Payment Rails ‚Äî Selective disclosure for auditors.
DeFi Rails for Regulated Entities ‚Äî For those who cannot use fully transparent chains.
üÜî Private Identity & Credentials
Identity Verification ‚Äî Prove age, citizenship, or credentials without revealing documents.
Private KYC/AML ‚Äî Compliance without data exposure.
Anonymous Reputation Systems ‚Äî Build trust without doxxing.
Credential Wallets ‚Äî Store and selectively disclose certifications.
üó≥Ô∏è Private Governance & Voting
Anonymous Voting ‚Äî Vote without revealing your choice.
Private DAOs ‚Äî Governance where member holdings stay confidential.
Whistleblower Systems ‚Äî Report safely with cryptographic protection.
Private Polls and Surveys ‚Äî Gather honest data without surveillance.
üß† Privacy-Preserving AI & Data
Private ML Inference ‚Äî Run AI models on encrypted data.
Confidential Data Marketplaces ‚Äî Sell data without exposing it.
Private Analytics ‚Äî Aggregate insights without individual tracking.
Secure MPC Protocols ‚Äî Collaborate without sharing raw data.
üåê Private Social & Communication
Anonymous Social Networks ‚Äî Express freely without surveillance.
Private Messaging ‚Äî Verify sender without revealing identity.
Confidential Content Platforms ‚Äî Monetize without exposure.
Private Professional Networks ‚Äî Network without revealing employer data.
You can port an existing project and rebuild it privacy-first on Aleo ‚Äî or design something that only makes sense in a world where privacy is the default.

Judging Criteria
Category	Weight	Focus
Privacy Usage	40%	Does it take advantage of Aleo‚Äôs privacy-preserving capabilities?
Technical Implementation	20%	How well-engineered is it?
User Experience	20%	How smooth is the UI/UX ?
Practicality and Real-World Use Case	10%	Is it actually practical in a real-world setting?
Novelty / Creativity	10%	How novel of an application is it in regards to either the Aleo ecosystem, or privacy-focused applications as a whole?
